name: Forever You
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | "Forever You" (2021) is a digital painting partly created through a GAN and my own brush strokes in Photoshop. It is the second work in my series "Thresholds". A 'threshold' can be a boundary or a starting point of an experience. I like its connection to the words 'thresh,' meaning "to separate seed from a plant using a machine" and 'thrash,' meaning "to beat soundly or go over again and again."
